headline: What Analysts Think Is Shifting The Story For Federal Realty Investment Trust (FRT)
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust has just seen its fair value estimate nudged higher to US$112.45 from US$112.34, alongside a modestly lower discount rate of 8.05% from 8.08% and a slightly softer revenue growth assumption of 4.62% from 4.65%. These tiny tweaks reflect how analysts are balancing relatively solid recent sector commentary with fresh caution that shopping center fundamentals may be closer to a peak.
